                    <div
                      class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.18em] transition-colors focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-ring focus:ring-offset-2 border-transparent bg-secondary/65 text-secondary-foreground hover:bg-secondary/90 px-2 py-0.5 text-[9px]"
                    >
                      L / D / S / F
